::KitKat::

"Yes, cutting yourself is very bad. I'll give you the blade back if 
you promise not to cut yourself ever again."

She looked at Land Mine's wrists and saw the mech fluid dripping.
"Come on, let's go to the lab and get some dressing for you. Then, 
can we talk as to what is bothering you?"
